data.description: There’s no place like HOME! You will fall in love with this beautiful three bedroom two bath home located on .34 acres in Burnet TX with Colorado River access and close proximity to LBJ Lake!  The interior and exterior of this home has been meticulously cared for!  This great floor-plan offers plenty of amazing features to include all hard surface flooring throughout, eatin kitchen w/breakfast bar open to dining, a spacious living area, separate cornered garden tub with walk-in shower and a walk-in closet in the primary bedroom, walk-in closet also included in one of the secondary bedrooms, laundry/utility room, front-porch, covered back-porch, mature trees and shrubs, garden bed, goat fencing, 2 car carport with a storage shed, 2 additional storage sheds out back and much more!  Don’t miss your opportunity to tour this lovely HOME, schedule a tour today!  Home has been retrofitted!
